<br>
I'd support warriors haveing their def/off disc on seperate tables.  It solve a lot of your taunt problem with boss mobs.  You'd take less damage and the use of a offensive disc would put your damage about back to your normal damage and those hold aggro better 3 minutes out of 10.  It'd also let non tanking warriors go offensive more often and since not def disc, your dps on raids would go up.  <br>
<br>
Now to keep things useful and balanced I'd reduce <br>
LoH &amp; Harm Touch to 32 minutes by use of 5 aa points. <br>
Warrior offensive disc reduced to no loner then 20 minutes with use of 3 aa points.<br>
<br>
Had to lower your offensive disc reuse time down to atleast 20 minutes inorder to make it useful on raids while keeping it high enough to not ruin the dps advantage of monks and rogues and rangers.<br>
<br>
Had to lower the reuse time of LH and HT inorder to keep pal/sk competitive with warriors for exp groups.<br>
<br>
I'm praying that the new shields willn't allow clerics to be MT in exp grinds and praying they'll give a edge to the war/pal/sk for tanking with the warrior a slight bit ahead.  <br>
<br>
p.s.<br>
Yes many paladins are very concerned that verant has stated 2 clerics with the improvements on test can grind exp nicely.  If two clerics can exp grind decent in CT then I believe all tanks should be scared.  I'm totaly blown away by that statement from verant.  CT isn't a place you see 2 people of any class grouping and grinding exp.  <br>
<br>
I'd have thought if vi decided to have clerics go tanking that they'd at least restrict them to undead like cleric nukes and paladins are.   I also would have thought that the shield upgrades would have stayed between warrior/paladin/sk.<br>
<br>
1 last note about shield<br>
Both warriors and kinghts lose dps when useing shields.  war higher skill and knights better ratios leaves damage in the air.  However the taunt % will aid warriors more for pal/sk don't need more taunt unless oom which we make sure almost never happens.  A rough guess I'd say if ghetto bashing warriors gain aggro as about the same margin paladins improve dps in comparision with the warrior being the better meat shield.<br>
