<br>
Doubt you could run a marathon in it, but you could put up a decent fight for a few seconds. Remember, all those long lasting standup fights you see on tv are just Hollywood. The human body provides a 20 second spurt of adrenaline for your average fight. I guess thats why its best to stay on your horse. heh heh<br>
<br>
Theres really no way to equate RP and historical reasons to why EQ works the way it does and the plight of warriors. Id hate to think that the reason I have low DPS and cant hold aggro that well is because Verant thinks my armor is heavy and the monster cant hear me through my mask... =/ <p><center><img src=http://www.netset.com/~blazer/zummy2.jpg></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=141&stop=160>8</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=161&stop=180>9</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=181&stop=200>10</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=201&stop=220>11</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=907.topic&start=221&stop=240>12</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange